  "text": "The common inhibitor of MAPK cascade, PD98059, was purchased from Sigma-Aldrich (Shanghai, China). Before SA treatment, the detached leaves were pre-incubated with PD98059 (dissolved in DMSO) for 60 min, and the final concentration of PD98059 was 150 µM [CITATION_1] .",
